OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 03 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1968FTWW ceases broadcasting.
OL,7,
OL,8,FThe station lost its franchise in the
OL,9,Fprevious ITV licensing awards and
OL,10,Fdecided to close 10 weeks early. It
OL,11,Fsold its remaining airtime to HTV for
OL,12,F#500,000.
OL,13,
OL,14,FHowever Harlech was not ready to
OL,15,Fcommence transmissions. To fill the
OL,16,Fgap, an interim service, staffed by
OL,17,Fformer TWW staff, was provided until
OL,18,FHarlech's launch on Monday 20th May
OL,19,F1968.
OL,20,
OL,21,
